---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Our Board Game Club"
	description="Join our community of board game enthusiasts for weekly gaming sessions and special events"
	pubDate={new Date('March 20 2024')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-3.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Welcome to our Board Game Club, where dice rolls and strategy meet friendship and fun! Founded in 2020, 
		we've grown from a small group of enthusiasts to a vibrant community of over 100 active members. Our club 
		meets every Thursday evening and Sunday afternoon, providing the perfect space for both casual and 
		competitive gaming experiences.
	</p>

	<p>
		Our collection features over 200 carefully curated board games, ranging from classic family favorites to 
		modern strategy masterpieces. Whether you're a fan of cooperative games like Pandemic and Spirit Island, 
		or prefer competitive classics like Catan and Ticket to Ride, you'll find your perfect match here. We 
		regularly update our library through member donations and club purchases, ensuring there's always something 
		new to explore.
	</p>

	<p>
		Beyond regular gaming sessions, we organize monthly tournaments, themed game nights, and special events. 
		Our annual "Game-A-Thon" charity event has raised over $5,000 for local causes, bringing together gamers 
		for 24 hours of continuous play. We also host beginner-friendly learning sessions where experienced 
		members teach popular games to newcomers, making sure everyone feels welcome regardless of their 
		experience level.
	</p>

	<p>
		The heart of our club lies in our diverse and inclusive community. Our members range from students to 
		retirees, all united by their love of board games. We've seen friendships form, strategies develop, and 
		countless memorable moments unfold across our gaming tables. Whether you're looking to master complex 
		strategy games or simply want to meet new people in a fun, relaxed environment, there's a place for you 
		here.
	</p>

	<p>
		Ready to join us? Membership is open year-round, with flexible options for both regular and occasional 
		participants. Drop by one of our open gaming sessions to experience the fun firsthand, or contact us 
		through our social media channels for more information. Come roll the dice with us and become part of 
		our growing board game community!
	</p>

	<div class="image-gallery">
		<img src="/preview3.webp" alt="Members enjoying a strategic board game session" class="gallery-image" />
		<img src="/preview4.webp" alt="Our extensive collection of board games" class="gallery-image" />
	</div>

	<style>
		.image-gallery {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
			margin-top: 2rem;
		}
		.gallery-image {
			width: 48%;
			height: auto;
			border-radius: 8px;
			object-fit: cover;
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
